Package compiler.symboltable

Class SymbolTable

java.lang.Object
compiler.symboltable.SymbolTable
public class SymbolTable extends Object
Encapsulates information about different symbols found when compiling a high-level-language program. The Symbol Table stores information about each Symbol that must be unique. For the sake of the implementation's completeness, RuntimeExceptions are thrown when information about unknown symbols is requested and when duplicate entries are added.
Author:
Alex Mandelias
